                     <interp inst="t18300916-70-person691" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. The prisoner was delivered to me with the box.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. Please your Worship, three or four boys stood by my side; I was going to my sister's, who kept a gingerbread stall at the fair - I was looking at a show; the gentleman pulled me out, and said he took the box from my hand - it was never in my hand.</p>
               <p>One witness gave the prisoner a good character.</p>
